snippet.title: Welcome to Goodland — Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: In Welcome to Goodland, players will find themselves in a small, peaceful town where they must navigate the dangerous world of money laundering. But as they climb the ranks and gain power, they must also answer whether they can maintain their humanity in this cutthroat world. Wishlist the game on Steam and don't miss the free demo next week → https://bit.ly/WtG_RDT
